{"tid":1588350,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【木棉花】香港革命旗幟芻議","createTime":"2019-09-22T18:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:37:41.000Z","uid":196839,"like":30,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b852a026be786d71c3927025fbe6a959ffd070e3","tid":1588350,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHGeyLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHGeyLn.jpg&h=99a8c294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n符號：五個人字並排，圍成一圈，寓意香港人祖先來自五湖四海，但今生今世聚首一堂，為家國前途搏盡無悔，<span style=\"color: orange;\">同心同德，堅毅不屈。</span>眾人團結一致，從內核迸發出力量。此外，圖案外形宛如一朵朵綻放嘅木棉花；木棉又稱「英雄樹」，係香港土生品種，寄意香港如大樹般，<span style=\"color: orange;\">雄姿英發，莊敬自強。</span><br />\n<br />\n圖案係攬炒旗嘅變奏：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRHA2Ai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRHA2Ai.png&h=64db1a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅棉見得多，其實木棉亦有黃色品種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8Sxkqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8Sxkqw.jpg&h=99c986e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybqCwxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybqCwxc.jpg&h=8ee77dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面色：金黃，象徵<strong>平等</strong>和<strong>團結</strong>。寓意香港人同舟共濟，不分化不割蓆，從團結找到力量。另外，此亦呼應香港盾徽內，兩艘黃色舢舨在碧海上乘風破浪。<br />\n<br />\n底色：普魯士藍，象徵<strong>自由</strong>和<strong>本土</strong>。圖案下方有着波浪，凸顯自由港嘅海洋性格，亦呼應李小龍嘅「若水」哲學以及2019年嘅流水革命。<br />\n<br />\n黃藍兩色係舊香港旗個龍獅盾徽嘅主色，在此用上除咗配搭富美感之餘，亦顯示歷史傳承。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Hong_Kong_Independence_Movement_Flag.svg/1200px-Hong_Kong_Independence_Movement_Flag.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F01%2FHong_Kong_Independence_Movement_Flag.svg%2F1200px-Hong_Kong_Independence_Movement_Flag.svg.png&h=ee990b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢面旗結構、用色簡單，小朋友都畫得出，有象徵意義，亦能呼應時代精神，同時能用寥寥數語概括深邃含義：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">意義｜自由、平等、團結、本土<br />\n符號｜眾人、木棉花、海洋</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n尺寸：150x100cm<br />\npsd檔案下載連結：<a href=\"https://gofile.io/?c=huSOvz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgofile.io%2F%3Fc%3DhuSOvz&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=4e653781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gofile.io/?c=huSOvz</a><br />\n高清圖檔，歡迎自由取用"},{"pid":"69c82d0acf3ac7968ab48b98bc2a70f593853290","tid":1588350,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"eaf1592f518e77ad293412557620f7f099636130","tid":1588350,"uid":89595,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:38:56.000Z","msg":"好撚正 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3704e7615f355debc7edf3fa8d7cccc10b6150","tid":1588350,"uid":69753,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:43:42.000Z","msg":"幾好嘅<br />\n好過呢堆傻閪旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbp0uo4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frbp0uo4.jpg&h=ae0d3be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPVbA34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPVbA34.jpg&h=405eadee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHoXwCp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.